  "transliteration": "tasmāc chāstraṁ pramāṇaṁ te kāryākārya-vyavasthitau\njñātvā śhāstra-vidhānoktaṁ karma kartum ihārhasi",
  "translation": "Therefore, scripture is your authority in determining what should be done and what should not be done. Knowing this, you should act accordingly.",
